1. *Pišem* pismo svojoj baki. (I am writing a letter to my grandmother.)
2. On *piše* knjigu o srpskoj istoriji. (He is writing a book about Serbian history.)
3. *Napiši* svoje ime na papiru. (Write your name on the paper.)
4. Njena sestra *piše* pesme. (Her sister writes poems.)
5. Učiteljica *piše* na tabli. (The teacher is writing on the blackboard.)
6. Mladić *piše* na svom blogu o putovanjima. (The young man is writing on his travel blog.)
7. Kada *budem pisao* diplomski rad, posvetiću ga roditeljima. (When I write my thesis, I will dedicate it to my parents.)
8. Prošle godine *sam pisao* pismo žalbe našoj kompaniji. (Last year, I wrote a complaint letter to our company.)
9. Jelena *je pisala* roman tri godine. (Jelena wrote the novel for three years.)
10. Oni *će pisati* ispit iz srpskog jezika sutra. (They will write a Serbian language exam tomorrow.)